    "Driver experience is categorised as either a novice driver (one to three years), an intermediate driver (four to six years), or an experienced driver (over six years).",
    "This is consistent with (Commonwealth of Massachusetts, 2023; Robbins & Chapman, 2019).",
    "Our study investigated the relationship between driving experience and the proficiency with which participants engaged with ADAS.",
    "This is outlined in Tables 6 and 7 for the conventional and ChatGPT learning groups, respectively.",
    "Our findings concur with (Murtaza et al., 2023) that increased driving experience corresponds to improved performance in activating ADAS functions."
